originalText.text: I was planning on using one of the more popular NYC moving companies before running into Mike & EJ on the street. They not only provided a fair quote, but gave me tips on what to prepare for my move BEFORE I even decided to hire them. On the day of, they came well prepared and made moving a breeze. I can't recommend EJ and his company enough. Although I hope not to move again for a while, I'll be sure to contact them when the time comes! :)

originalText.text: Very professional from start to finish. Jack was pleasant and easy to work with, even when I had to change my move date. Pricing was and scope of service was explained thoroughly. They moved me quickly and efficiently, and handled my things with the care. Moving me in was just as efficient. They asked considerate questions to make sure everything was going in the right places. All amazing personalities that made the move feel like a great time with friends. They will be my first call should I need to move again.

originalText.text:
Ido and his guys were fantastic.  They showed up on time and worked none stop to move 2 apartments into a house. They secured everything and put everything where needed to go. The cost was half of what any other company charges . I highly recommend them.
I will definitely use them again!
Very reliable, responsive, professional, great value!

originalText.text: The service was amazing!! I called and received a quote and booked within 48 hrs. I had a strict early morning move time and I even texted at 6:30am to make sure he was awake because I could afford any mistakes or severe lateness and everything was so blissful!!! They were actually early and very professional and coherent with my instructions of what to take as I left and met them at the drop off site which was a brutal 5 flight walk up that they tackled effortlessly!! The best moving company I’ve used and I’ve moved 3 times. Can’t wait to use them again in the next couple weeks

originalText.text: Excellent moving service. Quick at getting COI for both buildings and very responsive leading up to my move. Showed up on time and got the job done quickly with disassembly and reassembly. Will definitely use them again and highly recommend.
